data.description: Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this meticulously crafted designer home caters to those with a taste for refined living. Step inside through the impressive Alder wood front door, and you'll be welcomed into a spacious and inviting foyer that seamlessly connects to a private guest wing, a formal dining area, and an open-concept kitchen, living, and dining space. The formal dining area will undoubtedly become a cherished space for hosting memorable events with friends and loved ones. The living area exudes an air of sophistication with its 9 ft high coffered ceiling and floor-to-ceiling windows, which amplifies the sense of space. A cozy corner gas log fireplace adds a touch of comfort, making it an ideal spot for relaxation and unwinding. The kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with an oversized center island, generous prep space, ample storage, and top-of-the-line finishes and fixtures. The elegant granite countertops perfectly compliment the rich wood custom cabinetry, stylish tile backsplash, and designer lighting. The owner's suite exudes sophistication with a chic accent wall, a high ceiling, bay window, and an abundance of dreamy natural light. Unwind in the spa-like ensuite bath featuring dual vanities, a jetted tub, and a walk-in shower. The main floor guest wing comprises 2 bedrooms and a full bath. Ascend the gorgeous staircase to the expansive 2nd-floor, offering versatility as a fourth bedroom, game room, private office, or more, complete with another full bath. For year-round entertaining, the screened-in patio provides the perfect setting with a double ceiling fan, space for a table or lounge area, and easy access to the alfresco portion of the patio. The backyard offers a tranquil retreat after a long day or a space to host vibrant gatherings with friends and family. Conveniently situated just mins away from HEB, Leander hospital, Metro Rail, ACC campus, and 183A, this home is ideally located for all your needs.
